---
import SkillLayer from "./SkillLayer.astro";


---

<div class="w-full py-8 px-4 md:px-48 mt-24 md:mt-48 border-t border-white/20">
      <div class="flex flex-col w-full items-center p-4">
            <div class="scale-90 opacity-90 flex flex-row items-center gap-4 font-thin border border-white/30 bg-white/5 w-fit px-1 md:px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
                  My Skills :>
            </div>
            <h2 class="w-full text-center mt-4 text-6xl font-bold">Engineering <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-accent from-purple-600 to-purple-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Capabilities</span></h2>
            <p class="max-w-154 text-center mt-4 text-base md:text-lg font-semibold opacity-75">I love exploring new technolgies! I believe honing my skills in new areas gives some insights on how each of them works and what makes them uniquely different from others</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 w-full flex flex-col gap-4 items-center">
            <SkillLayer 
                  abbreviation="UX"
                  title="User Experience Layer"
                  description="The purpose of a website is to get visited by customers, and you don't want them to leave bad impression, right?"
                  skillsets={[
                        "Canva",
                        "Figma",
                        "TailwindCSS",
                        "Motion.dev",
                        "AnimeJS"
                  ]}
            />
            <SkillLayer 
                  abbreviation="API"
                  title="Application Logic Layer"
                  description="Of course, we have to use atleast basic API architecture in order to make the system secure and expectable"
                  skillsets={[
                        "Rust",
                        "PHP",
                        "Javascript",
                        "Golang",
                        "Python",
                        "Dart"
                  ]}
            />
            <SkillLayer 
                  abbreviation="DB"
                  title="Storage Management Layer"
                  description="Data is one of the most important aspect regardless the industry. Data is precious!"
                  skillsets={[
                        "PostgreSQL",
                        "MySQL",
                        "SurrealDB",
                        "MongoDB",
                        "Redis"
                  ]}
            />
            <SkillLayer 
                  abbreviation="OPS"
                  title="Development & Infrastructure Layer"
                  description="As the project gets bigger, It will be better to make it more reliable, and easy to develop, deploy and maintain"
                  skillsets={[
                        "Github",
                        "Docker",
                        "Kubernetes",
                        "Cloudflare"
                  ]}
            />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 opacity-80 p-4 font-semibold text-center w-full border border-white/20 bg-purple-700/40 rounded-2xl">
            Each layer is designed to integrates with each other as a one performant system- <span class="text-purple-300">not isolated, falling apart application :)</span>
      </div>
</div>